infos.info: From OTRR's Wiki for First Lines entry on Counterspy: ';There is a conflict of episode titles starting on April 26, 1949 thru November 17, 1949 because in addition to the regularly scheduled ABC broadcasts, CBS rebroadcast Counterspy episodes on Tuesdays & Thursdays also. There will be separate entries for ABC & CBS shows. Notations will be made in the descriptions identifying the network of the show.(bk)'; - Ben Kibler is trying to identify all the CBS broadcasts for the series in 1949. Check out OTRR's Wiki for First Lines entry on Counterspy to see the results of his efforts. - ----------------------------------- - (5/26/2009) Ben Kibler, as a result of his research, has recommended some changes in the dates in the Broadcast History which have been made.
